  <description type="morphology">Stems 5–12 cm. Inflorescences con-tinuous from bases of branches or stems, narrowly cylindric, 2–10 × 5–7 mm; bracts appressed, elliptic-lanceolate, 4–8 mm, rigid, margins flat, green, if white then scarious portion 0.1–0.2 mm wide; lateral and midveins prominent adaxially. Flowers: perianth 2.1–2.9 mm; tube 29–40% of perianth length; tepals white or pink; perianth tube and base of tepals smooth; stamens 5–8. Achenes dark brown, lanceolate, 2–2.5 mm, reticulately ridged to almost smooth, dull.</description>
